TY  - JOUR
TI  - Simulated Moments Estimation of Markov Models of Asset Prices
AU  - Duffie, Darrell
AU  - Singleton, Kenneth J.
AB  - [This paper provides a simulated moments estimator (SME) of the parameters of dynamic models in which the state vector follows a time-homogeneous Markov process. Conditions are provided for both weak and strong consistency as well as asymptotic normality. Various tradeoffs among the regularity conditions underlying the large sample properties of the SME are discussed in the context of an asset-pricing model.]
